@baseUrl = http://localhost:{{$dotenv BACKEND_PORT}}
@llmBaseUrl = {{$dotenv LLM_BASE_URL}}
@llmApiKey = {{$dotenv LLM_API_KEY}}

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List all tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets

### List tickets by status (open | in_progress | resolved)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets?status=open

### Get single ticket
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1

### Stream AI summary for a ticket
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tickets/1/summary

### Chat with support agent
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Hello, I need help with my account." }
  ]
}

### Discover available LLM models
GET {{llmBaseUrl}}/v1/models
Authorization: Bearer {{llmApiKey}}
